import { AppBar, Toolbar, Typography } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'

const Navbar = () => {
  return (
    <React.Fragment>
      <AppBar sx={{background: ""}}>
        <Toolbar>
          <Typography>LOGO</Typography>
        </Toolbar>
      </AppBar>
    </React.Fragment>
  )
}

export default Navbar
